{"tid":1534400,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟呢兩日罷工罷出個咩樣？","createTime":"2019-09-03T03:46:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T04:36:37.000Z","uid":125967,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b212ab2e88a3cfb1878f3d727fd860681ac03973","tid":1534400,"uid":125967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:46:55.000Z","msg":"淨係識睇住班中學生點點點<br />\n<br />\n好嬲呀又盛咁<br />\n<br />\n咁又點？<br />\n<br />\n吹左咁撚耐雞 罷兩日工<br />\n<br />\n而家似乜<br />\n<br />\n次次都要有人犧牲先有過百萬人<br />\n<br />\n屌<br />\n<br />\n慚唔慚愧呀"},{"pid":"cb6d30e6ae796d7cba5e36a73456c768577ac7cd","tid":1534400,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:47:00.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月8！到時見！</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5fe7aaf9c9e3f3725c4fc4f9802fada616605791","tid":1534400,"uid":285855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:49:34.000Z","msg":"我好忙咁工作緊po野嫁<br />\n<br />\n香港回歸未定案嫁<br />\n<br />\n借一下位, 純手動po請見諒<br />\n<br />\n侵侵叫大陸還清朝債卷<br />\n大陸唔肯還成10萬億美金<br />\n佢話前朝唔認佢要還<br />\n如果唔駛還唔認點解要還香港<br />\nbloomberg同台灣都有講, 點解香港無聲氣<br />\n還, 大陸還唔起<br />\n唔還我地仲係英殖地<br />\n如果借據美國買左我地係美殖地<br />\n就算還都應該係還俾有還錢的政府, 我地就係台灣人<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-08-29/trump-s-new-trade-war-weapon-might-just-be-antique-china-debt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2019-08-29%2Ftrump-s-new-trade-war-weapon-might-just-be-antique-china-debt&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFIICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=5be0c85f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-08-29/trump-s-new-trade-war-weapon-might-just-be-antique-china-debt</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zdS50W9Aq_Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.c